channel.title: [PI] - Can't change the quest tab text
channel.description:
I don't really like being spoon fed because I like to learn from just trying things out, but I've looked and searched in MOST of my relevant files, basically on the quest tab it says "Owners: Complexity" ... I want to change it to "Owners: Nathan & Lewis", as i've already said; I'm using a PI source and could just use a little help on what file to search for and stuff. Thanks in advance.
- Nathan

item.title: [PI] - Can't change the quest tab text
item.dc:creator: @Virgin Virgin
item.description:
@Virgin wrote:

Server sided: src\server\model\players\Client.java. Edit it there.
Client sided: Open RSInterface.java and edit it there.
Hoped this helped you.
